definition: to rob/to plunder/to seize by force/to coerce/calamity/abbr. for kalpa 劫波[jie2 bo1]
car/vehicle/CL:輛|辆[liang4]/machine/to shape with a lathe/Kangxi radical 159

sentences.english: Then the man drove away, apparently in a great hurry.
sentences.chinese: 然後，劫車人迫不及待地急馳而去。

sentences.english: I informed our insurance brokers as soon as the theft was reported.
sentences.chinese: 我一知道劫車的事就通知了我們的保險經紀人。
